---
import { GH_URL } from '../consts';
import TerminalWindow from './TerminalWindow.astro';
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span>Local-first · MIT · Beta</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Your unread is now read.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        A local CLI that turns <strong>Telegram chats, YouTube videos, web pages, and files</strong>
        into Markdown reports with citations — using whichever LLM you keep an API key for.
      </p>
      <div class="ctas">
        <a href="#quickstart" class="btn btn-primary">
          Install in 90 seconds
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href={GH_URL} class="btn btn-ghost" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 .5a12 12 0 0 0-3.8 23.4c.6.1.8-.3.8-.6v-2c-3.3.7-4-1.6-4-1.6-.5-1.4-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.1-.8.1-.8.1-.8 1.2.1 1.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 1.1 1.9 2.9 1.3 3.6 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.8-1.6-2.7-.3-5.5-1.3-5.5-6 0-1.3.5-2.4 1.2-3.3-.1-.3-.5-1.5.1-3.2 0 0 1-.3 3.3 1.3a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0c2.3-1.6 3.3-1.3 3.3-1.3.7 1.7.3 2.9.1 3.2.8.9 1.2 2 1.2 3.3 0 4.7-2.8 5.7-5.5 6 .4.3.8 1 .8 2v3c0 .3.2.7.8.6A12 12 0 0 0 12 .5z"/></svg>
          Star on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
      <ul class="hero-bullets">
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> Citations on every claim</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> SQLite on your disk</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> Any LLM provider</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-demo">
      <TerminalWindow title="~/projects">
<span class="m">$</span> <span class="b">unread</span> <span class="a">@ru_dev_news</span> <span class="m">--last-days 7 --report-language en</span>
<span class="ok">✓</span> Fetched 1,284 messages from <span class="a">@ru_dev_news</span> <span class="c">(6.2s)</span>
<span class="ok">✓</span> Map-reduce: 8 chunks → merged <span class="c">(12.4s · $0.07)</span>
<span class="ok">✓</span> Wrote <span class="a">~/.unread/reports/ru_dev_news/digest-2026-05-23.md</span>

<span class="c"># Top decisions</span>
- Migrate analytics off Segment by Q3 <span class="a">[#1586]</span>
- Roll out indexed funds policy in Q1 2026 <span class="a">[#1612]</span>

<span class="c"># Open questions</span>
- Who owns the migration runbook? <span class="a">[#1591]</span>

<span class="m">$</span> <span class="b">unread ask</span> <span class="a">@ru_dev_news</span> <span class="m">"What did Anna propose?"</span>
<span class="ok">✓</span> Anna proposed a phased migration with feature flags <span class="a">[#1604]</span>.
      </TerminalWindow>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 4.5rem 0 3rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(700px 320px at 80% 0%, var(--accent-soft), transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(800px 380px at 10% 100%, var(--accent-soft), transparent 70%);
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .hero { padding-top: 3rem; }
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .eyebrow .dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--success);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--success);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--fg) 30%, color-mix(in oklab, var(--fg) 70%, var(--accent)));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
    max-width: 56ch;
  }
  .lead strong { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 600; }
  .ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  }
  .hero-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .hero-bullets li {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .check {
    color: var(--success);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
